User Story:
As an employee, I want to access a user-friendly portal, so that I can submit my maternity leave requests online without relying on emails.
Acceptance Criteria:

The portal allows employees to log in using single sign-on (SSO).
Employees can fill out and submit a maternity leave request form with required fields.
The portal confirms submission via a success message and email notification.

User Story:
As an HR administrator, I want employees to submit leave requests through the ServiceNow portal, so that I can reduce manual processing and keep all requests centralized.
Acceptance Criteria:

All submitted requests are visible in the ServiceNow dashboard.
HR administrators can filter requests by status (e.g., pending, approved, rejected).
Manual email submission is disabled after portal implementation.
